<h2 id="四阻尼振动与受迫振动" class="heading">四、阻尼振动与受迫振动<a href="#四阻尼振动与受迫振动" class="heading-anchor" aria-label="Heading Anchor"><i class="iconfont icon-link"></i></a></h2>
